summary: Wood Elf character I made, a modest attempt at a \"cute\" elf.
descriptionHtml:
This is a save file I uploaded from the beginning of the game right after you go into the keep. You will start with Raloff in the first room. 

Mods running when creating this that you will need. 

Cover Women by mrLenski http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3563
Cover Eyes  by mrLenski http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4869

I took heavily from looking at how he made his elf\'s look for his screen shots, I hope this does them justice. Thanks -
author: Ironhelix4
